T(n) = | O(1),             n = 0
       | T(n - 1) + O(1), n >= 1

T(n) <= T(n - 1) + C <=
     <= (T(n - 2) + C) + C <= 
     <= T(n - 3) + 3C <= ...
      = C*n+C  = O(n)
     
