T(n) = | O(1),             n = 0
       | T(n - 1) + O(n), n >= 1       

T(n) <= T(n - 1) + C*n <=
     <= (T(n - 2) + C*(n-1)) + C*n <= 
     <= (T(n - 3) + C*(n-2))+C*(n-1)+C*n <= ...
    <= ะก + ะก*(n+(n-1)+(n-2)+...+1) =
    = C*(n*(n-1)/2+1) = O(n**2)

      
